    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "It's a great idea, though I see MC as highly different in many aspects not related merely to graphics:\n- pre-mission loadout: choice of starting units, their equipment, pilots;\n- critical hits: random effects caused by damage;\n- accuracy: based not only on weapon spread, but also by target's movement;\n- multiple hit zones: torso, head, arms, legs...related to critical hits;\n- salvaging: shouldbe also related to criticals;\n- movement modes: run, walk, jump;\n\nsome of these things can be made in the state of the engine, but not the menus, in-game loadouts and criticals... or am I wrong?\n"
